      <button
        type="button"
        class="py-2 px-4 inline-flex items-center gap-x-2 text-sm font-medium text-nowrap rounded-lg border border-transparent bg-blue-600 text-white hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-hidden focus:bg-blue-700 transition disabled:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none cursor-pointer">
        Записаться
